{
  "stem": "7546.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they received such a beating in the Soviet Union, they didn't have anyone to save them, and it was already after VE Day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were being beaten in the west, and they lost the east.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in Auschwitz, I was there for about eight to nine days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the man that was in charge of the barracks said that everyone that came here must tell him and he will register you-- what you are, whether you're a tailor, whether you are a bricklayer, whether you are a shoemaker-- whatever your profession is, whatever your trade is.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a very dear friend-- I still have him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's also in Israel, now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a bricklayer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't want to part with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And his father was a bricklayer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he says, you know, why don't you tell him that you're a bricklayer, so maybe we'll go together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which, I did and saved my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I became a bricklayer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And about a week or eight days later, we were put in a transport going to Braunschweig, Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't get numbers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did get numbers on the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got numbers-- my number was 50,554.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went into the train, from Auschwitz to the train, and went all the way to Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Braunschweig is a town near Hanover.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Braunschweig, the part of the town called [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH] were two camps, empty camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was only one barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were 150 in the transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were assigned to build barracks for new prisoners that will be coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I became a bricklayer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was doing very well as a bricklayer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I learned a trade and I was good at it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
